        <options>
            <option letter="a">State labor laws</option>
            <option letter="b">Immigration quotas</option>
            <option letter="c">Voting reforms</option>
            <option letter="d">Banking regulation</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>Florence Kelley's advocacy led to state-level labor laws protecting women and children workers, including maximum hours and minimum wage legislation.</explanation>
